hopobject.body: Canada>Canada womensinternational.com/refills.html While we love her belt and shoes and bag it's the shorts we are jonesing for. That high waist and big box pleat at the front - they're super sophisticated and smart and ever so 1940s. They're from one of Kourtney's favourite brands, FindersKEEPERS which happily is available over here depsite it being Australian. You can find it at Harrods or online at Shopbop but annoyingly these shorts aren't stocked here as yet.
